item.title: Sources: Sof.uz
item.description: Launched in 2016, Sof.uz is a digital news publication designed to deliver news to a wider audience using accessible language.

item.title: Sources: CABAR
item.description: Founded in 2016 and based under the Institute’s for War and Peace Reporting (IWPR) Central Asian Office, Central Asian Bureau for Analytical Reporting (CABAR) offers regional analytical, informational, and educational material on Central Asia.

item.title: Sources: TengriNews
item.description: Founded in 2016, TengriNews offers news coverage of current events in Kazakhstan and the world and a database of legislative documents.
